@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = YOUR_TOKEN

### Create Daily Recurring Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Morning Exercise",
  "description": "30 minutes workout",
  "priority": "high",
  "dueDate": "2024-12-18T07:00:00Z",
  "recurring": {
    "enabled": true,
    "frequency": "daily",
    "interval": 1
  }
}

### Create Weekly Recurring Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Team Meeting",
  "description": "Weekly team sync",
  "priority": "medium",
  "dueDate": "2024-12-20T10:00:00Z",
  "recurring": {
    "enabled": true,
    "frequency": "weekly",
    "interval": 1,
    "endDate": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z"
  }
}

### Get All Recurring Tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/recurring
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Toggle Task Completion (Creates Next Occurrence)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/TASK_ID/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Manually Create Next Occurrence
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/TASK_ID/create-next
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
